Subject: [security bulletin] HPSBMU02781 SSRT100617 rev.2 - HP Network Node Manager i (NNMi) for HP-UX, Linux, Solaris, and Windows running PostgreSQL, Remote Execution of Arbitrary Code, Denial of Service (DoS)

